parameters:
Memimi: I'm terribly sorry... Boss...! To disgrace myself in
front of the audience, to tarnish the name of our
organization... and even more so... even more so...!

Shark Broccoli: Don't worry about it, Shark Duke... If you
couldn't win, then no one in our organization could have.
The outcome would have been the same. No one blames you...

Underling: That's right, Duke...! Even with your mask torn
and your true identity revealed, you fought valiantly... It
was splendid...!

Underling: Who would have thought that the Duke's true
identity was part-time worker Sameyama-san... I had no
idea... Mysterious and beautiful, you were my idol...

Memimi: Stop... don't look so much... It seems like it will
take quite some time to repair the mask, so I guess I have
no choice but to operate without it for a while... Now that
my identity has been exposed anyway, well, it's fine...

Shark Broccoli: Anyway, our organization is disbanding
today. But there's no need to be sad. From now on, let's
unite under a new organization and realize our dream of
dominating the city...

Memimi: Sigh... Boss... I would rather serve under you than
Anomalocaris...

Anomalocaris: Hey there, losers! Thanks for the welcome...
From now on, you'll be working hard as my subordinates!

Memimi: Grrr, such arrogance! Just because you defeated me
doesn't mean you can act all high and mighty in front of
Boss Shark Broccoli...
Memimi: Nghh... Ugh, no, my apologies...

Anomalocaris: Hmm hmm, you gotta watch your language with
your superiors! Hey, Shark Broccoli! Give me a shoulder rub!

Memimi: Nghaaaaaaah...! Ugh ugh... It's unbearable...!
Because of me... Ugh...

Anomalocaris: For now, you newbies also need to wear our
organization's underling suits, but we haven't managed to
get the order in yet. So for a while, keep working hard in
your current clothes.

Anomalocaris: However, we do have some outfits for female
members that were made a long time ago. You—wear this one...
We never had a single woman join our organization until
now... As our first female member, you'll be doing various
tasks, alright?

Memimi: ...Hmph, I lost, so it's my fault... I haven't come
to terms with it yet, but I'll listen to what you say...

Anomalocaris: Ohh... It suits you well! All the effort I put
into designing it was worth it...

Lackey: Damn, that's hot! To make Shark Duke wear such an
outfit!! And with her face revealed too... She's such a
beauty!!

Lackey: Whoo-whoo! Looks like we might see some panties! No
bra either, if she jumps a bit, we might see her boobs too!?

Memimi: You vulgar lot... Seriously, it's ridiculous. Don't
make such a fuss just because I changed into an outfit that
shows a bit of skin!

Underling: Shark Duke is so dignified and reliable...
Clearly being harassed with sexual harassment and yet not
showing any sign of being disturbed... Those bare legs
are... amazing...

Underling: She's one of the top executives of our battle-
hardened organization! Even if she were stripped naked,
nothing would change... Always calm under any circumstances,
we should all learn from her... Haa haa...

Memimi: (Aaargh... What is this slutty outfit!? My breasts
are almost showing... The underwear is like strings! How am
I supposed to walk in public like this!? Impossible
impossible impossible...!)

Anomalocaris: And then... You underlings who have become
part of my crew, former subordinates of Shark Broccoli, I
have prepared a new gig for you!! A splendid gig as dealers
of a certain product!!

Memimi: Wha... dealers? We are members of an underground
organization but under Boss Shark Broccoli's policy, we've
been thorough in not dealing with illegal goods...

Anomalocaris: It's the "Anomaro-kun Acrylic Key Holder"!!
Sell these to every person in the city! 600 yen each!

Memimi: There's not a shred of illegality but... to carry
around such things in bulk and peddle them to people on the
street...? It's becoming depressing...
For Memimi and her companions, hard days had begun...
'屈辱の敗北！モスマンタンクトップ装着の巻'
